{"tid":779634,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人靚仔便無敵","createTime":"2018-08-14T14:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T15:38:44.000Z","uid":175490,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d216c392dfcc1d631d8692b9afe9f8f80cb49f16","tid":779634,"uid":175490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人諗過靚仔真係玩撚曬<br />\n講工作 研究顯示靚仔比正常人人工高大概10%<br />\n講溝女 啲女寧願畀佢呃蝦條都仲中個頭埋去<br />\n我想講啲女係咪咁on9 明知正常靚仔( 除咗嗰啲自以為靚仔嘅仔)都唔會定性㗎啦 大部分都係玩完就走 啲女都仲要中個頭埋去俾佢屌/撚 <br />\n就算你正常樣 條女都係多數騎牛搵馬 一有靚仔嘅就成個衝埋去<br />\n毒撚都係疊埋心水一世打飛機算啦<br />\n利申 毒撚"},{"pid":"a24168feb16506348637f7178633c524255ab9b2","tid":779634,"uid":175490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"89b48af18fc592ab34c3fbf4551c610d42fb91c9","tid":779634,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"係咁㗎啦"},{"pid":"fd5bdd138e90d070cf943af9a849d9e542be8690","tid":779634,"uid":77569,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T14:43:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6c87ed12a9dc7a2757294c17772a0926f3c6396","tid":779634,"uid":176924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89b48af18fc592ab34c3fbf4551c610d42fb91c9","tid":779634,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"係咁㗎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T14:44:26.000Z","msg":"好出奇呀"},{"pid":"54e40e8bc37496b57f112c7269102e9aeb568ad0","tid":779634,"uid":3962,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"問題係靚同柒仔都係想呃蝦屌點解唔同好樣個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fcd1570a64c1e45727e215346fdde92a7e397f","tid":779634,"uid":175490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54e40e8bc37496b57f112c7269102e9aeb568ad0","tid":779634,"uid":3962,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"問題係靚同柒仔都係想呃蝦屌點解唔同好樣個個<im